{"id":22607,"date":"2019-11-15T18:01:47","date_gmt":"2019-11-15T11:01:47","guid":{"rendered":"\/?p=22607"},"modified":"2019-11-27T22:01:01","modified_gmt":"2019-11-27T15:01:01","slug":"thu-thuat-wordpress-huu-ich-cho-blogger","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"\/wordpress\/thu-thuat-wordpress-huu-ich-cho-blogger","title":{"rendered":"8 Th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 c\u1ef1c h\u1eefu \u00edch cho Blogger"},"content":{"rendered":"\n<p class=\"highlight\">C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00f3 xu h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a WordPress plugin tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi nh\u1eadn ra r\u1eb1ng b\u1ea1n ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 ch\u1ec9 b\u1eb1ng <strong>m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/strong>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn code &#8220;ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p&#8221;, kh\u00f4ng can thi\u1ec7p v\u00e0o h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng server &#8220;nguy hi\u1ec3m&#8221; v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam plugin &#8220;n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1&#8221;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress an to\u00e0n, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n h\u1eefu \u00edch cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi WordPress.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt \u0111\u1ed5i WordPress Admin username &#8220;m\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ecbnh&#8221;<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1eadt ra kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 c\u00f3&nbsp;<strong>username admin<\/strong>&nbsp;M\u1eb6C \u0110\u1ecaNH cho <a href=\"https:\/\/vi.wordpress.org\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Wordpress (opens in a new tab)\">WordPress<\/a>. Khi b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress th\u00ec b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o m\u1edbi username admin cho WordPress blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng t\u1ef1 c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress website m\u00e0 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 d\u1ecbch v\u1ee5 t\u1ea1o WordPress website hay \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 nh\u1edd b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o d\u00f9m.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o WordPress v\u1edbi username admin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o s\u1eb5n. Ti\u1ebft ki\u1ec7m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau th\u1eddi gian c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, sau \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i username admin b\u1edfi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 l\u00fd do nh\u01b0:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng website cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00e1c.<\/li><li>Mu\u1ed1n thay \u0111\u1ed5i username v\u00ec m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch b\u1ea3o m\u1eadt.<\/li><li>Mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ed5i username cho d\u1ec5 nh\u1edb v\u00e0 \u0111\u1eb9p h\u01a1n.<\/li><\/ul>\n\n\n\n<p>R\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc, WordPress&nbsp;<strong>kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p<\/strong>&nbsp;b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5i username nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed5i t\u00ean hay \u0111\u1ecba ch\u1ec9 email trong WordPress Admin Dashboard v\u00ec n\u00f3 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn WordPress user database.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ec3 gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 n\u00e0y, b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c plugin. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ed4I ADMIN USERNAME GI\u00c1N TI\u1ebeP.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>C\u00e1ch th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n WordPress User m\u1edbi v\u1edbi username \u0111\u1eb7t nh\u01b0 \u00fd mu\u1ed1n c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/li><li>C\u1ea5p quy\u1ec1n Admin cho t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3.<\/li><li>\u0110\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n m\u1edbi t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 xo\u00e1 \u0111i t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n admin c\u0169.<\/li><li>T\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng, WordPress s\u1ebd chuy\u1ec3n to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 user database sang t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n m\u1edbi t\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"935\" height=\"669\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi.png\" alt=\"Tao Tai Khoan Admin Moi\" class=\"wp-image-22661\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi.png 935w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi-218x156.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi-300x215.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi-700x501.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Tao-tai-khoan-admin-moi-768x550.png 768w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 935px) 100vw, 935px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>1. T\u1ea1o t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Admin m\u1edbi<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-1024x444.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"444\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-1024x444.png\" alt=\"Xoa Tai Khoan Admin Cu\" class=\"wp-image-22662\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-1024x444.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-218x94.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-300x130.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-700x303.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu-768x333.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/xoa-tai-khoan-admin-cu.png 1608w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>2. Xo\u00e1 t\u00e0i kho\u1ea3n Admin c\u0169<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-1024x578.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"578\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-1024x578.png\" alt=\"Chuyen Doi Tat Ca Bai Viet Sang Admin Moi Tao\" class=\"wp-image-22663\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-1024x578.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-700x395.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao-768x433.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-doi-tat-ca-bai-viet-sang-admin-moi-tao.png 1173w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>3. Chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft sang Admin m\u1edbi t\u1ea1o v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t vi\u1ec7c chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i<\/figcaption><\/figure><\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Ch\u00e8n link trong Author Info (Biographical Info)<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng cu\u1ed1i m\u1ed7i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t Author Box \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3n th\u1ecb th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 (th\u01b0\u1eddng theme s\u1ebd h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3). Th\u00f4ng tin n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y t\u1eeb User Profile trong&nbsp;<strong>Biographical Info<\/strong>&nbsp;c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf ch\u1ed7 l\u00e0 khung \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1n \u0111\u00fang ngh\u0129a l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec. Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u00f4ng c\u1ee5 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ch\u00e8n link hay h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh, c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 d\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u1ea1ng n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0ng may m\u1eafn, <strong>Biographical Info<\/strong> \u00edt ra c\u0169ng ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn HTML link.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 khi n\u00e0o b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n ch\u00e8n link b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng HTML c\u01a1 b\u1ea3n&nbsp;<code>&lt;a&gt;<\/code>&nbsp;tag \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00e8n v\u00e0o. B\u1ea1n h\u00e3y xem v\u00ed d\u1ee5 sau \u0111\u00e2y:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<pre class=\"wp-block-code\"><code>&lt;a href=\"https:\/\/facebook.com\/pagecuaban\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook&lt;\/a> \u00b7 &lt;a href=\"https:\/\/https:\/\/facebook.com\/group\/idgroupcuaban\" rel=\"nofollow\">Facebook Group&lt;\/a><\/code><\/pre>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"442\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-1024x442.png\" alt=\"Khung Dien Tieu Su Cua Tac Gia WordPress\" class=\"wp-image-22665\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-1024x442.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-218x94.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-300x130.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-700x302.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress-768x332.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khung-dien-tieu-su-cua-tac-gia-Wordpress.png 1366w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea1n \u0111i\u1ec1n v\u00e0o khung Biographical Info<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-1024x200.png\" alt=\"Ket Qua Ban Se Duoc Author Box Nhu The Nay\" class=\"wp-image-22666\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-1024x200.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-218x43.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-300x59.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-700x137.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay-768x150.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Ket-qua-ban-se-duoc-author-box-nhu-the-nay.png 1861w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd c\u00f3 link li\u00ean k\u1ebft nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0y trong \u00f4 T\u00e1c gi\u1ea3<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n n\u00ean d\u00f9ng <code>nofollow atribute<\/code> cho m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i (ngo\u00e0i ra th\u00ec c\u1ee9 d\u00f9ng dofollow) nh\u01b0 tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh g\u00e2y h\u1ea1i cho SEO blog c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n v\u00ec outbound link li\u00ean k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ebfn Facebook kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb cho SEO m\u00e0 c\u00f2n t\u00e1c d\u1ee5ng ng\u01b0\u1ee3c.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng&nbsp;<code>&lt;b&gt;<\/code>&nbsp;tag \u0111\u1ec3 in \u0111\u1eadm.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t h\u1eefu \u00edch khi b\u1ea1n Guest Post hay ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn Guest Post v\u1edbi th\u00f4ng tin t\u00e1c gi\u1ea3 back link v\u1ec1 website c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Thay \u0111\u1ed5i giao di\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ti\u1ebfng Anh cho user<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Khi c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress th\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef cho g\u00f3i c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t. Th\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t cho th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng Vi\u1ec7t Nam.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Sau \u0111\u00f3 WordPress s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng chuy\u1ec3n giao di\u1ec7n <strong>WP-Admin<\/strong> sang ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-1024x471.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"471\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-1024x471.png\" alt=\"Giao Dien Tieng Viet WordPress\" class=\"wp-image-22667\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-1024x471.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-218x100.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-700x322.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress-768x353.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/giao-dien-tieng-viet-wordpress.png 1920w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Giao di\u1ec7n WP-Admin ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t \u0111\u00f4i khi kh\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ti\u1ec7n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, khi b\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n b\u00e1o c\u00e1o l\u1ed7i cho nh\u00e0 ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n theme hay plugin th\u00ec b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng giao di\u1ec7n WP-admin ti\u1ebfng Anh cho user u\u1ef7 quy\u1ec1n (h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u0103ng nh\u1eadp v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda l\u1ed7i cho b\u1ea1n).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ho\u1eb7c trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed5i sang giao di\u1ec7n WP-Admin ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec7n l\u00e0m theo nh\u1eefng h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c blog n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u0169ng v\u1eady, n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n thu\u00ea ng\u01b0\u1eddi n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i qu\u1ea3n l\u00fd website hay thao t\u00e1c tr\u00ean website b\u1ea1n, th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Anh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i c\u00e0i l\u1ea1i WordPress ti\u1ebfng Anh?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, WordPress cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t giao di\u1ec7n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho t\u1eebng ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng (user) m\u1ed9t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>V\u00e0o user profile m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i giao di\u1ec7n.<\/li><li>Ch\u1ecdn language sang <strong>ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/strong> v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"467\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-1024x467.png\" alt=\"Chuyen Sang Ngon Ngu Tieng Anh\" class=\"wp-image-22668\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-1024x467.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-218x100.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-300x137.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-700x320.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-768x351.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-sang-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh.png 1908w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Chuy\u1ec3n sang ng\u00f4n ng\u1eef ti\u1ebfng Anh cho ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng Admin. <br>B\u1ea5m c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt h\u1ed3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t!<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"471\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-1024x471.png\" alt=\"Cap Nhat Xong Ngon Ngu Tieng Anh\" class=\"wp-image-22669\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-1024x471.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-218x100.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-300x138.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-700x322.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh-768x353.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cap-nhat-xong-ngon-ngu-tieng-Anh.png 1902w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt xong giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Nh\u01b0 b\u1ea1n th\u1ea5y, t\u00f4i th\u01b0\u1eddng c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t giao di\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfng Anh khi h\u01b0\u1edbng d\u1eabn b\u1ea1n s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng cho ti\u1ec7n v\u00ec c\u00e1c thu\u1eadt ng\u1eef WordPress n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ebfng Anh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00e1c b\u1ea1n m\u1edbi c\u00f3 ngay n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng khi mu\u1ed1n ti\u1ebfp thu ki\u1ebfn th\u1ee9c n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>N\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress g\u00f3i ti\u1ebfng Anh th\u00ec s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00f9y ch\u1ecdn &#8220;ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t&#8221;. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t WordPress ti\u1ebfng Vi\u1ec7t th\u00ec s\u1ebd c\u00f3.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Ch\u00e8n n\u00fat &#8220;Button&#8221; v\u00e0o Menu \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n d\u00f9ng Plugin<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u00e8n n\u00fat b\u1ea5m (button) v\u00e0o thanh \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u01b0\u1edbng gi\u00fap Menu blog b\u1ea1n tr\u1edf n\u00ean chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ed5i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c theme tr\u1ea3 ph\u00ed th\u01b0\u1eddng cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh ch\u00e8n &#8220;button&#8221; nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng cao c\u1ea5p.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress sau \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng h\u1ea7u nh\u01b0 v\u1edbi m\u1ecdi <a href=\"\/wordpress\/top-theme-wordpress-ban-hang-va-blogging\/\">theme WordPress mi\u1ec5n ph\u00ed<\/a> ch\u1ec9 v\u1edbi v\u00e0i d\u00f2ng HTML \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>C\u1ee9 th\u00eam Menu nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/li><li>Ch\u00e8n th\u00eam&nbsp;<code>class button<\/code>&nbsp;cho \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng link li\u00ean k\u1ebft. B\u1ea1n th\u00eam nh\u01b0 sau&nbsp;<code>&lt;span class=\"button\"&gt;Menu Item&lt;\/span&gt;<\/code>. B\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng&nbsp;<code>&lt;span&gt;<\/code>&nbsp;tag \u0111\u1ec3 nh\u00e3n nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng. Thay&nbsp;<code>Menu Item<\/code>&nbsp;th\u00e0nh nh\u00e3n Menu m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-1024x476.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"476\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-1024x476.png\" alt=\"Them Trang Bat Ky Vao Menu\" class=\"wp-image-22670\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-1024x476.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-218x101.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-300x139.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-700x325.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu-768x357.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Them-trang-bat-ky-vao-menu.png 1903w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>1. Th\u00eam Menu nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"478\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-1024x478.png\" alt=\"Theme Class Button Vao Menu\" class=\"wp-image-22671\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-1024x478.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-218x102.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-300x140.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-700x327.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu-768x358.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/theme-class-button-vao-menu.png 1142w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Th\u00eam HTML code &#8220;nh\u1eb9&#8221; v\u00e0o nh\u00e3n c\u1ee7a Menu<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"539\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-1024x539.png\" alt=\"Thanh Qua Sau Khi Them Menu\" class=\"wp-image-22672\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-1024x539.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-218x115.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-300x158.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-700x369.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu-768x404.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thanh-qua-sau-khi-them-Menu.png 1548w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>B\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 th\u00eam Button v\u00e0o Menu v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110i\u1ec3m c\u1ed1t y\u1ebfu c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o button FAKE. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf n\u00f3 ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t Menu b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e0 ph\u1ee7 l\u00ean di\u1ec7n m\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t n\u00fat button.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n, an to\u00e0n, kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng g\u00ec v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Ngo\u00e0i ra, n\u1ebfu tinh \u00fd b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00fat Button inline cho c\u1ea3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft si\u00eau g\u1ecdn l\u1eb9.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110a s\u1ed1 c\u00e1c WordPress theme \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n <code>class button<\/code> n\u00ean h\u00e3y t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng class button c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb9o tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh: b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh button b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch th\u00eam ID ri\u00eang thay v\u00ec t\u1ea1o m\u1ed9t&nbsp;<code>class button<\/code>&nbsp;m\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh n\u1edf file CSS.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 d\u00f9ng&nbsp;<strong>CSS Classes (optional)<\/strong>&nbsp;trong tu\u1ef3 ch\u1ec9nh Menu WordPress b\u1edfi v\u00ec b\u1ea1n s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra n\u00fat Button c\u1ef1c x\u1ea5u v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00fang.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-1024x415.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"415\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-1024x415.png\" alt=\"Khong Dung Css Classes\" class=\"wp-image-22674\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-1024x415.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-218x88.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-300x122.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-700x284.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes-768x311.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/khong-dung-css-classes.png 1270w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Kh\u00f4ng d\u00f9ng CSS Classes c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">T\u1ea1o smooth scroll trong b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft blog nh\u01b0 Page Builder<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 quen v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c d\u00f9ng Page Builder \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o link hay n\u00fat b\u1ea5m m\u00e0 m\u1ed7i khi nh\u1ea5p v\u00e0o s\u1ebd t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng ch\u1ea1y xu\u1ed1ng m\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ecbnh (nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a M\u1ee5c L\u1ee5c).<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 khi b\u1ea1n t\u1ea1o trang v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ee7a Page Builder plugin. C\u00f2n trong Post, l\u00e0m th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng Page Builder \u0111\u1ec3 vi\u1ebft post?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00e0i \u0111\u1eb7t th\u00eam plugin WordPress?<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt ch\u1ec9nh ch\u00fat x\u00edu m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng Smooth Scroll b\u1ea1n b\u1eaft bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i c\u00f3:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Link k\u00edch ho\u1ea1t v\u1edbi URL l\u00e0&nbsp;<code>#id<\/code>&nbsp;(ID nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o do b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1eb7t)<\/li><li>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c&nbsp;<strong>ID Selector<\/strong>.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<p>T\u1ea1o link li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u00f3 URL th\u00ec d\u1ec5, b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng, sau \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00e8n URL b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng&nbsp;<code>#<\/code>&nbsp;m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. V\u00ed d\u1ee5:&nbsp;<code>#demuc1<\/code>&nbsp;hay&nbsp;<code>#CTA<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"485\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-1024x485.png\" alt=\"Chen Link Nhu Binh Thuong\" class=\"wp-image-22675\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-1024x485.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-218x103.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-300x142.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-700x332.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong-768x364.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chen-link-nhu-binh-thuong.png 1294w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u00e8n link nh\u01b0 b\u00ecnh th\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0ng b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1eb1ng #<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u1ec1 vi\u1ec7c g\u00e1n&nbsp;<code>ID class<\/code>&nbsp;th\u00ec c\u0169ng kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. Gutenberg block ch\u1ec9 cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n th\u00eam&nbsp;<code>Class<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00ec v\u1eady b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng m\u1ed9t t\u00fd x\u1ea3o thu\u1eadt.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n chuy\u1ec3n block \u0111\u00f3 th\u00e0nh HTML b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch b\u1ea5m v\u00e0o d\u1ea5u 3 ch\u1ea5m v\u00e0 ch\u1ecdn&nbsp;<strong>Edit as HTML<\/strong>. Th\u00eam&nbsp;<code>id=\"giongvoiURLtren\"<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0o trong tag&nbsp;<code>&lt;&gt;<\/code>.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>V\u00ed d\u1ee5:&nbsp;<code>&lt;h2&gt;De muc #1&lt;\/h2&gt;<\/code>&nbsp;\u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00eam ID th\u00e0nh&nbsp;<code>&lt;h2 id=\"demuc1\"&gt;De muc #1&lt;\/h2&gt;<\/code>&nbsp;v\u00e0 ho\u00e0n t\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cach-them-id-vao-gutenberg-block.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1113\" height=\"626\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/cach-them-id-vao-gutenberg-block.gif\" alt=\"Cach Them Id Vao Gutenberg Block\" class=\"wp-image-22677\"\/><\/a><figcaption>C\u00e1ch th\u00eam ID v\u00e0o Gutenberg Block<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho m\u1ecdi Gutenberg block t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 kh\u00e1 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>B\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o ID v\u00e0 link URL sau d\u1ea5u # l\u00e0 gi\u1ed1ng nhau.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Th\u1ec9nh tho\u1ea3ng b\u1ea1n c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169 \u0111\u1ec3 SEO t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, nh\u01b0ng cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m b\u1ea1n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng. B\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n PH\u1ee4C H\u1ed2I l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169 c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch n\u00e0o.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng Auto Save, WordPress lu\u00f4n t\u1ef1 \u0111\u1ed9ng sao l\u01b0u khi b\u1ea1n nh\u1ea5n v\u00e0o n\u00fat Save Draft, Publish hay Update.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1c b\u1ea3n sao l\u01b0u n\u00e0y \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9ng cho nh\u1eefng tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n v\u00e0o Revision &gt; Ch\u1ecdn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5 h\u1ed3i &gt; b\u1ea5m &#8220;<strong>Restore this Revision<\/strong>&#8220;.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"499\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-1024x499.png\" alt=\"Revision Trong WordPress Post\" class=\"wp-image-22678\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-1024x499.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-218x106.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-300x146.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-700x341.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post-768x374.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Revision-trong-Wordpress-post.png 1573w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u1ecdn Revision \u1edf Sidebar<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Revision-can-phuc-hoi.gif\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1695\" height=\"744\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/Chon-Revision-can-phuc-hoi.gif\" alt=\"Chon Revision Can Phuc Hoi\" class=\"wp-image-22679\"\/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u1ecdn phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 l\u01b0u m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mong mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Revision cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n so s\u00e1nh ngay phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i v\u00e0 phi\u00ean b\u1ea3n mu\u1ed1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i \u0111\u1ec3 b\u1ea1n ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"tip\"><span class=\"title\">Ch\u00fa \u00dd<\/span>\n<p>Khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u0169 th\u00ec ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c WordPress s\u1ebd c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n v\u1eeba ph\u1ee5c h\u1ed3i l\u00e0 Revision M\u1edaI NH\u1ea4T. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng, khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ed5i \u00fd mu\u1ed1n Redo l\u1ea1i b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u1edbi l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. B\u1ea1n c\u1ea7n ch\u1ecdn cho \u0111\u00fang.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">\u0110\u00ednh m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u trang &#8211; Sticky Post<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t quan tr\u1ecdng hay mang t\u00ednh th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 lu\u00f4n n\u1eb1m \u1edf top, k\u1ec3 c\u1ea3 c\u00e1c b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft m\u1edbi xu\u1ea5t b\u1ea3n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm \u0111\u00e2u xa, ngay trong WordPress c\u00f3 t\u00edch h\u1ee3p s\u1eb5n t\u00ednh n\u0103ng n\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00f2n cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u trang thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>C\u00e1ch l\u00e0m nh\u01b0 sau:<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>Edit b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft b\u1ea1n mu\u1ed1n<\/li><li>Ch\u1ecdn Status &amp; Visibility<\/li><li>Ch\u1ecdn&nbsp;<strong>Sticky Post<\/strong><\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"473\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-1024x473.png\" alt=\"Chon Vao Sticky Post\" class=\"wp-image-22681\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-1024x473.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-218x101.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-300x139.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-700x324.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post-768x355.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-vao-sticky-post.png 1581w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>Ch\u1ecdn Sticky Post \u1edf &#8220;Status &amp; Visibility&#8221;<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft, c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m l\u00e0 t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"pk-heading-numbered\">Export c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng xu\u1ea5t file (export) c\u1ee7a WordPress kh\u00f4ng cho ph\u00e9p b\u1ea1n xu\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 n\u00e0o. Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c quy\u1ec1n xu\u1ea5t h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft d\u1ef1a theo b\u1ed9 l\u1ecdc ti\u00eau chu\u1ea9n nh\u01b0 Category.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u1ea1n th\u00ec \u0111ang mu\u1ed1n xu\u1ea5t c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 nh\u1eb1m m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch \u0111\u1ec3 Guest Post hay th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m tr\u00ean m\u1ed9t website kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>M\u1eb9o xu\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 c\u00fang kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. B\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch d\u00f9ng k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt L\u1eccC DUY NH\u1ea4T.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<ol><li>B\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n xu\u1ea5t sang&nbsp;<strong>Private<\/strong>.<\/li><li>V\u00e0o export<\/li><li>Ch\u1ecdn Status l\u00e0&nbsp;<strong>Private<\/strong>&nbsp;v\u00e0 xu\u1ea5t.<\/li><li>Quay l\u1ea1i chuy\u1ec3n b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea1i Public nh\u01b0 c\u0169.<\/li><\/ol>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"464\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-1024x464.png\" alt=\"Chuyen Bai Viet Muon Export Sang Private\" class=\"wp-image-22682\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-1024x464.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-218x99.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-300x136.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-700x317.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private-768x348.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chuyen-bai-viet-muon-export-sang-private.png 1605w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>1. Chuy\u1ec3n b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft mu\u1ed1n Export sang Status l\u00e0 &#8220;Private&#8221;<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-1024x577.png\"><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"577\" src=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-1024x577.png\" alt=\"Chon Status Private\" class=\"wp-image-22683\" srcset=\"https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-1024x577.png 1024w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-218x123.png 218w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-700x395.png 700w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private-768x433.png 768w, https:\/\/cdn.cuongthach.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/chon-status-private.png 1564w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/a><figcaption>2. Ch\u1ecdn Status l\u00e0 &#8220;Private&#8221; v\u00e0 b\u1ea5m n\u00fat Download<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>B\u00e2y gi\u1edd b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft xu\u1ea5t ra \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 mong mu\u1ed1n b\u1edfi v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft l\u00e0 \u1edf tr\u1ea1ng th\u00e1i Private m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n v\u00e0 b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng cho c\u1ea3 Page v\u1edbi c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<h2>L\u1eddi k\u1ebft&#8230;.<\/h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Hi v\u1ecdng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y s\u1ebd gi\u00fap b\u1ea1n bi\u1ebft th\u00eam \u00edt nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec m\u1edbi m\u1ebb trong 8 th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt WordPress t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb \u1edf tr\u00ean.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed t\u00e0i nguy\u00ean hay dung l\u01b0\u1ee3ng cho nh\u1eefng g\u00ec WordPress \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n cho b\u1ea1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>\u0110\u00f4i khi b\u1ea1n \u0111\u1ecdc m\u1ed9t b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft \u0111\u00e3 c\u0169 v\u00e0 l\u00e0m theo m\u00e0 b\u1ea1n kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng WordPress ng\u00e0y nay t\u1ef1 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n, an to\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh ch\u1ec9 d\u1eabn n\u1ebfu b\u1ea1n c\u00f2n v\u01b0\u1edbng m\u1eafc h\u00e3y \u0111\u00e2u \u0111\u00f3 h\u1eaby \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i ph\u1ea7n b\u00ecnh lu\u1eadn b\u00ean d\u01b0\u1edbi nh\u00e9!<\/em><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 m\u1eb9o v\u00e0 th\u1ee7 thu\u1eadt Wordpress \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 d\u00e0nh cho nh\u1eefng b\u1ea1n Blogger m\u1edbi.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":17,"featured_media":22686,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"close","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[42],"tags":[46],"featured_image_urls":{"full":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger.png",1024,512,false],"thumbnail":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger-300x150.png",270,135,true],"medium":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger-700x350.png",700,350,true],"medium_large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger-768x384.png",768,384,true],"large":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger.png",1024,512,false],"1536x1536":["\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/11\/thu-thuat-wordpress-don-gian-ma-cuc-huu-ich-cho-blogger.png",1024,512,false],